\begin_layout Subsection*
Visual Cheat Sheet:
 The Collection Hierarchy
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
Note:
 When in doubt,
 start with an immutable 
\family typewriter
List
\family default
.
 If you need to search by key,
 move to a 
\family typewriter
Map
\family default
.
 If you need uniqueness,
 use a 
\family typewriter
Set
\family default
.
 The standard library makes it trivial to convert between them using 
\family typewriter
.toList
\family default
,
 
\family typewriter
.toMap
\family default
,
 or 
\family typewriter
.toSet
\family default
.
\end_layout

